{"tid":917871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"正妹教師愛上19歲校長兒　索討買車錢遭勒斃慘死河中","createTime":"2018-11-26T17:40:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T08:26:47.000Z","uid":212399,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d2dd8f5e6f58ebcb5b9b20f2958b2ddf05c5dacc","tid":917871,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T17:40:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3721/d3721726.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3721%2Fd3721726.jpg&h=1947b4f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女老師愛上19歲校長兒子，遭勒死棄屍。<br />\n俄羅斯一名27歲的英文老師科羅連科（Anastasia Khrolenko）於前年因婚姻破裂，進而與19歲的學生，同時也是校長兒子里巴切科（Dmitry Rybalchenko）交往。沒想到兩人發生爭執，里巴切科疑似無力償還買車費，將女友勒死再丟入河中製造假車禍，全案於上周被判入獄9年11個月。<br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，女老師科羅連科於2016年與丈夫離婚，接著與校長的兒子里巴切科交往，還曾借錢供年輕男友買機車。科羅連科在2016年10月與里巴切科外出約會，將女兒交給前夫亞歷山大（Alexander Khrolenko）照顧，卻再也連絡不上。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3721/d3721729.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3721%2Fd3721729.jpg&h=c067a65d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n殺害女友的里巴切科（Dmitry Rybalchenko）被判入獄9年11個月。<br />\n亞歷山大因找不到科羅連科立刻報警，當時警方也找不到這名女老師，經過半年後，才有漁民在中俄邊境的綏芬河（Razdolnaya）中看見科羅連科的屍體。經調查後發現，當時里巴切科開車載女友至橋上，並將科羅連科活活勒死，再用石頭敲擊頭部，接著開車輾過，試圖製造假車禍，隨後再將屍體丟入河中。<br />\n調查人員表示，里巴切科因向被害人借錢買機車被要求還錢，一時氣憤釀成殺機。里巴切科被逮捕後坦言，是自己殺害了女友科羅連科，原因為「私人仇恨」才犯案。<br />\n里巴切科向警方說明並模擬部分犯案過程，包括如何勒死女友，以及如何將手機燒毀，並於上周被判入獄服刑9年11個月。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9opkV-WpJ4k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9opkV-WpJ4k&d=vA4sQDXCDDAR0qQJMRgtOHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=44dfacbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9opkV-WpJ4k</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181126/1315892.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20181126%2F1315892.htm&d=vA4sQDXCDDAR0qQJMRgtOHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=89e6e8cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181126/1315892.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4c54b3f353d3415f2bf7c64409be294ea8f6b094","tid":917871,"uid":212399,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T17:42:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f5e8c260f6f36ac6bb93b728817c7da446b3e78","tid":917871,"uid":85232,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T17:57:20.000Z","msg":"on9仔有得屌都唔屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37874eb39bf871bb00133a246dcf520b764b277","tid":917871,"uid":100347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T18:33:04.000Z","msg":"樓上又知冇屌過 佢一定識人啦"},{"pid":"14e4f00ab8f21d06124f6297385148dea442d786","tid":917871,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f5e8c260f6f36ac6bb93b728817c7da446b3e78","tid":917871,"uid":85232,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T17:57:20.000Z","msg":"on9仔有得屌都唔屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T19:44:00.000Z","msg":"毒撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1994573535a108f92967047ad347280ef050e792","tid":917871,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T19:45:27.000Z","msg":"正撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c49af796ecec22db8fa4c8b25bc97cb5b17658f","tid":917871,"uid":208722,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T19:58:45.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯狗真係畜牲嚟，同支那一樣"},{"pid":"321fe280c32daaf63a704e7ad2b453ca70cadcb1","